'''少教多學'''（{{lang-en|'''Teach Less, Learn More'''，縮寫作'''TLLM'''}}）是一個[[教育哲學|教育哲學]]概念，由時任[[新加坡|新加坡]]總理的[[李顯龍|李顯龍]]於2004年提出<ref>{{cite journal |title=Teach Less, Learn More?  Unravelling the Paradox with People Development |language=en |year=2006 |journal=APERA Conference 2006 |date=2006-11-30 |url=http://edisdat.ied.edu.hk/pubarch/b15907314/full_paper/1115649590.pdf |author1=KOH, Yong Chiah |author2=LIM, Fei Victor |author= |access-date=2013-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075753/http://edisdat.ied.edu.hk/pubarch/b15907314/full_paper/1115649590.pdf |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。這個概念現時亦為其他國家所採納<ref>{{cite web |url=http://womany.net/read/article/2630 |title=芬蘭教育這樣改：教得愈少、學得愈多 |date=2013-04-01 |accessdate=2013-08-06 |language=zh-hant |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130610054149/http://womany.net/read/article/2630 |archive-date=2013-06-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。這個概念，關鍵在於透過培養學生的[[基礎學習能力|基礎學習能力]]來提高他們[[繼續學習|繼續學習]]的意願<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.taaze.tw/sing.html?pid=11100642778 |title=芬蘭教育這樣改！全球第一個教改成功案例教我們的事 / Finnish Lessons：What can the world learn from educational change in Finland? |year=2013 |publisher=[[讀冊生活|讀冊生活]] |language=zh-hant |access-date=2013-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130405043921/http://www.taaze.tw/sing.html?pid=11100642778 |archive-date=2013-04-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

